29вҶ’|------|------|------|------|------|\n    30вҶ’| **Plan** | `rick plan \"йңҖжұӮ\"` | з”ЁжҲ·йңҖжұӮ | task*.md | и§„еҲ’д»»еҠЎдёҺдҫқиө–е…ізі» |\n    31вҶ’| **Doing** | `rick doing job_n` | task*.md | д»Јз Ғ+debug.md | жү§иЎҢд»»еҠЎе№¶и®°еҪ•й—®йўҳ |\n    32вҶ’| **Learning** | `rick learning job_n` | debug.md+gitеҺҶеҸІ | OKR/SPEC/Wikiжӣҙж–° | зҹҘиҜҶз§ҜзҙҜдёҺдјҳеҢ– |\n    33вҶ’\n    34вҶ’### 1.4 е…ій”®ж–Үд»¶ж јејҸи§„иҢғ\n    35вҶ’\n    36вҶ’#### task.mdпјҲд»»еҠЎе®ҡд№үпјү\n    37вҶ’```markdown\n    38вҶ’# дҫқиө–е…ізі»\n    39вҶ’task1, task2\n    40вҶ’\n    41вҶ’# д»»еҠЎеҗҚз§°\n    42вҶ’еҲӣе»ә server.go жәҗж–Үд»¶\n    43вҶ’\n    44вҶ’# д»»еҠЎзӣ®ж Ү\n    45вҶ’еҹәдәҺgRPCжЎҶжһ¶пјҢе®ҢжҲҗgRPC Serverзҡ„жҗӯе»әе·ҘдҪң\n    46вҶ’\n    47вҶ’# е…ій”®з»“жһң\n    48вҶ’1. жЈҖжҹҘжҳҜеҗҰе·Іе®үиЈ…gRPCжңҖж–°зүҲжң¬\n    49вҶ’2. жЈҖжҹҘGoзүҲжң¬жҳҜеҗҰж»Ўи¶іжңҖж–°gRPCиҰҒжұӮ\n    50вҶ’3. жҹҘйҳ…gRPCжңҖж–°зүҲжң¬Serverжһ„е»әж–ҮжЎЈ\n    51вҶ’4. зј–еҶҷGolangд»Јз Ғпјҡе®һзҺ°дёҖдёӘgRPC Hello WorldеӨ„зҗҶеҮҪж•°\n    52вҶ’5. зЎ®дҝқд»Јз ҒйҖҡиҝҮlintжЈҖжҹҘ\n    53вҶ’\n    54вҶ’# жөӢиҜ•ж–№жі•\n    55вҶ’1. еӯҰд№ gRPCжңҚеҠЎз«ҜеҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ•и§„иҢғ\n    56вҶ’2. зј–еҶҷеҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ•пјҡеҗҜеҠЁServerпјҢеҸ‘иө·RPCиҜ·жұӮ\n    57вҶ’3. иҝҗиЎҢеҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ•пјҡ`go test -v ./...`\n    58вҶ’```\n    59вҶ’\n    60вҶ’#### tasks.jsonпјҲд»»еҠЎDAGпјү\n    61вҶ’```json\n    62вҶ’[\n    63вҶ’    {\n    64вҶ’        \"task_id\": \"task1\",\n    65вҶ’        \"task_name\": \"зҺҜеўғжЈҖжҹҘдёҺдҫқиө–е®үиЈ…\",\n    66вҶ’        \"dep\": [],\n    67вҶ’        \"state_info\": {\"status\": \"pending\"}\n    68вҶ’    },\n    69вҶ’    {\n    70вҶ’        \"task_id\": \"task2\",\n    71вҶ’        \"task_name\": \"еӯҰд№ gRPCжңҖдҪіе®һи·ө\",\n    72вҶ’        \"dep\": [\"task1\"],\n    73вҶ’        \"state_info\": {\"status\": \"pending\"}\n    74вҶ’    }\n    75вҶ’]\n    76вҶ’```\n    77вҶ’\n    78вҶ’#### debug.mdпјҲй—®йўҳи®°еҪ•пјү\n    79вҶ’```markdown\n    80вҶ’# debug1: еҹҹеҗҚи§ЈжһҗеӨұиҙҘ\n    81вҶ’\n    82вҶ’**й—®йўҳжҸҸиҝ°**\n    83вҶ’ж— жі•з§‘еӯҰдёҠзҪ‘пјҢж— жі•и§Јжһҗgithub.comеҹҹеҗҚ\n    84вҶ’\n    85вҶ’**и§ЈеҶізҠ¶жҖҒ**\n    86вҶ’е·Іи§ЈеҶі\n    87вҶ’\n    88вҶ’**и§ЈеҶіж–№жі•**\n    89вҶ’- step1: еҗҜеҠЁproxy.shй…ҚзҪ®д»ЈзҗҶ\n    90вҶ’- step2: ping github.comйӘҢиҜҒиҝһйҖҡжҖ§\n    91вҶ’```\n    92вҶ’\n    93вҶ’### 1.5 е·ҘдҪңз©әй—ҙз»“жһ„\n    94вҶ’\n    95вҶ’```\n    96вҶ’.rick/                          # е…ЁеұҖдёҠдёӢж–ҮпјҲдәәзұ»жҠҠжҺ§пјү\n    97вҶ’в”ңв”Җв”Җ OKR.md                      # йЎ№зӣ®е…ЁеұҖзӣ®ж Ү\n    98вҶ’в”ңв”Җв”Җ SPEC.md                     # йЎ№зӣ®ејҖеҸ‘и§„иҢғ\n    99вҶ’в”ңв”Җв”Җ wiki/                       # йЎ№зӣ®зҹҘиҜҶеә“\n   100вҶ’в””в”Җв”Җ skills/                     # еҸҜеӨҚз”ЁжҠҖиғҪеә“\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"54120658-0f38-420a-a12a-de4bb8dc43a6","uuid":"d9f26bb1-feea-4f64-85e9-501e624bd7f8","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/sunquan/ai_coding/CODING/rick/.morty/research/дҪҝз”Ё_golang_ејҖеҸ‘_rick_е‘Ҫд»ӨиЎҢзЁӢеәҸ.md","content":"# дҪҝз”Ё Golang ејҖеҸ‘ Rick е‘Ҫд»ӨиЎҢзЁӢеәҸ - и°ғз ”жҠҘе‘Ҡ\n\n**и°ғжҹҘдё»йўҳ**: дҪҝз”Ё Golang ејҖеҸ‘ Rick е‘Ҫд»ӨиЎҢзЁӢеәҸ\n**и°ғз ”ж—Ҙжңҹ**: 2026-03-13\n\n---\n\n## 1. йЎ№зӣ®жҰӮиҝ°\n\n### 1.1 йЎ№зӣ®зұ»еһӢ\n- **дё»йЎ№зӣ®**: RickпјҲзҗҶи®әжЎҶжһ¶дёҺи®ҫи®Ўи§„иҢғпјү\n- **еҸӮиҖғе®һзҺ°**: MortyпјҲGoиҜӯиЁҖе®һзҺ°пјү\n- **жң¬ж¬Ўз ”з©¶**: Rick CLI зҡ„ Go е®һзҺ°\n\n### 1.2 Rick йЎ№зӣ®ж ёеҝғе®ҡд№ү\n\nRick жҳҜдёҖдёӘ**Context-First AI Coding Framework**пјҢж ёеҝғзҗҶи®әпјҡ\n```\nAICoding = Humans + Agents\nе…¶дёӯ Agents = Models + Harness\nHarness еҢ…еҗ«дёӨдёӘеҸҚйҰҲеҫӘзҺҜпјҡ\n1. Agent Loop: UI вҶ’ Model вҶ’ ToolsпјҲClaude Codeе·Іе®һзҺ°пјү\n2. Context Loop: Plan вҶ’ Doing вҶ’ LearningпјҲRickйңҖиҰҒе®ҢжҲҗпјү\n```\n\n### 1.3 Rick зҡ„дёүдёӘж ёеҝғйҳ¶ж®ө\n\n| йҳ¶ж®ө | е‘Ҫд»Ө | иҫ“е…Ҙ | иҫ“еҮә | зӣ®зҡ„ |\n|------|------|------|------|------|\n| **Plan** | `rick plan \"йңҖжұӮ\"` | з”ЁжҲ·йңҖжұӮ | task*.md | и§„еҲ’д»»еҠЎдёҺдҫқиө–е…ізі» |\n| **Doing** | `rick doing job_n` | task*.md | д»Јз Ғ+debug.md | жү§иЎҢд»»еҠЎе№¶и®°еҪ•й—®йўҳ |\n| **Learning** | `rick learning job_n` | debug.md+gitеҺҶеҸІ | OKR/SPEC/Wikiжӣҙж–° | зҹҘиҜҶз§ҜзҙҜдёҺдјҳеҢ– |\n\n### 1.4 е…ій”®ж–Үд»¶ж јејҸи§„иҢғ\n\n#### task.mdпјҲд»»еҠЎе®ҡд№үпјү\n```markdown\n# дҫқиө–е…ізі»\ntask1, task2\n\n# д»»еҠЎеҗҚз§°\nеҲӣе»ә server.go жәҗж–Үд»¶\n\n# д»»еҠЎзӣ®ж Ү\nеҹәдәҺgRPCжЎҶжһ¶пјҢе®ҢжҲҗgRPC Serverзҡ„жҗӯе»әе·ҘдҪң\n\n# е…ій”®з»“жһң\n1. жЈҖжҹҘжҳҜеҗҰе·Іе®үиЈ…gRPCжңҖж–°зүҲжң¬\n2. жЈҖжҹҘGoзүҲжң¬жҳҜеҗҰж»Ўи¶іжңҖж–°gRPCиҰҒжұӮ\n3. жҹҘйҳ…gRPCжңҖж–°зүҲжң¬Serverжһ„е»әж–ҮжЎЈ\n4. зј–еҶҷGolangд»Јз Ғпјҡе®һзҺ°дёҖдёӘgRPC Hello WorldеӨ„зҗҶеҮҪж•°\n5. зЎ®дҝқд»Јз ҒйҖҡиҝҮlintжЈҖжҹҘ\n\n# жөӢиҜ•ж–№жі•\n1. еӯҰд№ gRPCжңҚеҠЎз«ҜеҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ•и§„иҢғ\n2. зј–еҶҷеҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ•пјҡеҗҜеҠЁServerпјҢеҸ‘иө·RPCиҜ·жұӮ\n3. иҝҗиЎҢеҚ•е…ғжөӢиҜ•пјҡ`go test -v ./...`\n```\n\n#### tasks.jsonпјҲд»»еҠЎDAGпјү\n```json\n[\n    {\n        \"task_id\": \"task1\",\n        \"task_name\": \"зҺҜеўғжЈҖжҹҘдёҺдҫқиө–е®үиЈ…\",\n        \"dep\": [],\n        \"state_info\": {\"status\": \"pending\"}\n    },\n    {\n        \"task_id\": \"task2\",\n        \"task_name\": \"еӯҰд№ gRPCжңҖдҪіе®һи·ө\",\n        \"dep\": [\"task1\"],\n        \"state_info\": {\"status\": \"pending\"}\n    }\n]\n```\n\n#### debug.mdпјҲй—®йўҳи®°еҪ•пјү\n```markdown\n# debug1: еҹҹеҗҚи§ЈжһҗеӨұиҙҘ\n\n**й—®йўҳжҸҸиҝ°**\nж— жі•з§‘еӯҰдёҠзҪ‘пјҢж— жі•и§Јжһҗgithub.comеҹҹеҗҚ\n\n**и§ЈеҶізҠ¶жҖҒ**\nе·Іи§ЈеҶі\n\n**и§ЈеҶіж–№жі•**\n- step1: еҗҜеҠЁproxy.shй…ҚзҪ®д»ЈзҗҶ\n- step2: ping github.comйӘҢиҜҒиҝһйҖҡжҖ§\n```\n\n### 1.5 е·ҘдҪңз©әй—ҙз»“жһ„\n\n```\n.rick/                          # е…ЁеұҖдёҠдёӢж–ҮпјҲдәәзұ»жҠҠжҺ§пјү\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ OKR.md                      # йЎ№зӣ®е…ЁеұҖзӣ®ж Ү\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ SPEC.md                     # йЎ№зӣ®ејҖеҸ‘и§„иҢғ\nв”ңв”Җв”Җ wiki/                       # йЎ№зӣ®зҹҘиҜҶеә“\nв””в”Җв”Җ skills/                     # еҸҜеӨҚз”ЁжҠҖиғҪеә“","numLines":100,"startLine":1,"totalLines":958}}},{"type":"assistant","message":{"role":"assistant","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0},"stop_reason":null,"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_c2496cba-aa3","type":"message","content":[{"text":"I see the issue. Job 6 is meant to test that Rick can use itself for self-refactoring, but the rick plan command requires Claude Code CLI which doesn't work in this environment. This is a known design limitation documented in Job 2.\n\nHowever, since Job 6 is testing the self-refactoring capability, let me take a different approach. Instead of using `rick plan`, I can manually create a task.md file and test the `rick doing` and `rick learning` workflow. Let me check what the actual test should be:\n\nLooking at the Job 6 requirements:\n1. Plan a refactoring task (using rick)\n2. Install development version (rick_dev)\n3. Execute the refactoring task (using rick)\n4. Verify refactoring with rick_dev\n5. Update production version\n6. Verify new version works\n7. Uninstall dev version\n\nSince the `rick plan` command has a design limitation, let me create the task manually and focus on testing the execution and verification workflow. Let me update the plan file to document this finding:","type":"text"}],"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"54120658-0f38-420a-a12a-de4bb8dc43a6","uuid":"10b40b4b-c631-4684-8f68-a6a957b6f140"},{"type":"assistant","message":{"role":"assistant","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0},"stop_reason":null,"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_c2496cba-aa3","type":"message","content":[{"input":{"file_path":"/Users/sunquan/ai_coding/CODING/rick/.morty/plan/e2e_test.md","offset":252,"limit":50},"name":"Read","id":"toolu_bdrk_01DWVvPmuyrhdNBYwgZGnenu","type":"tool_use"}],"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"54120658-0f38-420a-a12a-de4bb8dc43a6","uuid":"dc2209d6-4b27-4f48-913e-b2017f2e0910"},{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01DWVvPmuyrhdNBYwgZGnenu","type":"tool_result","content":"   252вҶ’### Job 6: иҮӘжҲ‘йҮҚжһ„иғҪеҠӣйӘҢиҜҒ\n   253вҶ’\n   254вҶ’#### зӣ®ж Ү\n   255вҶ’\n   256вҶ’йӘҢиҜҒ Rick CLI иғҪеӨҹдҪҝз”ЁиҮӘиә«иҝӣиЎҢйҮҚжһ„\n   257вҶ’\n   258вҶ’#### еүҚзҪ®жқЎд»¶\n   259вҶ’\n   260вҶ’- job_5 - жҖ§иғҪе’ҢзЁіе®ҡжҖ§жөӢиҜ•е®ҢжҲҗ\n   261вҶ’\n   262вҶ’#### Tasks\n   263вҶ’\n   264вҶ’- [ ] Task 1: дҪҝз”Ёз”ҹдә§зүҲжң¬ rick и§„еҲ’йҮҚжһ„д»»еҠЎ\n   265вҶ’- [ ] Task 2: е®үиЈ…ејҖеҸ‘зүҲжң¬ rick_dev\n   266вҶ’- [ ] Task 3: дҪҝз”Ёз”ҹдә§зүҲжң¬ rick жү§иЎҢйҮҚжһ„д»»еҠЎ\n   267вҶ’- [ ] Task 4: дҪҝз”ЁејҖеҸ‘зүҲжң¬ rick_dev йӘҢиҜҒйҮҚжһ„\n   268вҶ’- [ ] Task 5: жӣҙж–°з”ҹдә§зүҲжң¬ `./update.sh`\n   269вҶ’- [ ] Task 6: йӘҢиҜҒж–°зүҲжң¬еҠҹиғҪжӯЈеёё\n   270вҶ’- [ ] Task 7: еҚёиҪҪејҖеҸ‘зүҲжң¬\n   271вҶ’\n   272вҶ’#### йӘҢиҜҒеҷЁ\n   273вҶ’\n   274вҶ’- и§„еҲ’гҖҒжү§иЎҢгҖҒйӘҢиҜҒгҖҒжӣҙж–°жөҒзЁӢе®Ңж•ҙ\n   275вҶ’- иҮӘжҲ‘йҮҚжһ„жҲҗеҠҹе®ҢжҲҗ\n   276вҶ’- ж–°зүҲжң¬еҠҹиғҪжӯЈеёё\n   277вҶ’- зүҲжң¬жӣҙж–°ж— й”ҷиҜҜ\n   278вҶ’\n   279вҶ’#### и°ғиҜ•ж—Ҙеҝ—\n   280вҶ’\n   281вҶ’ж— \n   282вҶ’\n   283вҶ’#### е®ҢжҲҗзҠ¶жҖҒ\n   284вҶ’\n   285вҶ’вҸі еҫ…ејҖе§Ӣ\n   286вҶ’\n   287вҶ’---\n   288вҶ’\n   289вҶ’### Job 7: ж–ҮжЎЈе’ҢзӨәдҫӢйӘҢиҜҒ\n   290вҶ’\n   291вҶ’#### зӣ®ж Ү\n   292вҶ’\n   293вҶ’йӘҢиҜҒж–ҮжЎЈе®Ңж•ҙжҖ§е’ҢзӨәдҫӢд»Јз ҒжӯЈзЎ®жҖ§\n   294вҶ’\n   295вҶ’#### еүҚзҪ®жқЎд»¶\n   296вҶ’\n   297вҶ’- job_6 - иҮӘжҲ‘йҮҚжһ„иғҪеҠӣйӘҢиҜҒе®ҢжҲҗ\n   298вҶ’\n   299вҶ’#### Tasks\n   300вҶ’\n   301вҶ’- [ ] Task 1: йӘҢиҜҒ README.md ж–ҮжЎЈе®Ңж•ҙ\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"54120658-0f38-420a-a12a-de4bb8dc43a6","uuid":"a6197588-9e4a-4a34-918d-ebdee2b99120","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/sunquan/ai_coding/CODING/rick/.morty/plan/e2e_test.md","content":"### Job 6: иҮӘжҲ‘йҮҚжһ„иғҪеҠӣйӘҢиҜҒ\n\n#### зӣ®ж Ү\n\nйӘҢиҜҒ Rick CLI иғҪеӨҹдҪҝз”ЁиҮӘиә«иҝӣиЎҢйҮҚжһ„\n\n#### еүҚзҪ®жқЎд»¶\n\n- job_5 - жҖ§иғҪе’ҢзЁіе®ҡжҖ§жөӢиҜ•е®ҢжҲҗ\n\n#### Tasks\n\n- [ ] Task 1: дҪҝз”Ёз”ҹдә§зүҲжң¬ rick и§„еҲ’йҮҚжһ„д»»еҠЎ\n- [ ] Task 2: е®үиЈ…ејҖеҸ‘зүҲжң¬ rick_dev\n- [ ] Task 3: дҪҝз”Ёз”ҹдә§зүҲжң¬ rick жү§иЎҢйҮҚжһ„д»»еҠЎ\n- [ ] Task 4: дҪҝз”ЁејҖеҸ‘зүҲжң¬ rick_dev йӘҢиҜҒйҮҚжһ„\n- [ ] Task 5: жӣҙж–°з”ҹдә§зүҲжң¬ `./update.sh`\n- [ ] Task 6: йӘҢиҜҒж–°зүҲжң¬еҠҹиғҪжӯЈеёё\n- [ ] Task 7: еҚёиҪҪејҖеҸ‘зүҲжң¬\n\n#### йӘҢиҜҒеҷЁ\n\n- и§„еҲ’гҖҒжү§иЎҢгҖҒйӘҢиҜҒгҖҒжӣҙж–°жөҒзЁӢе®Ңж•ҙ\n- иҮӘжҲ‘йҮҚжһ„жҲҗеҠҹе®ҢжҲҗ\n- ж–°зүҲжң¬еҠҹиғҪжӯЈеёё\n- зүҲжң¬жӣҙж–°ж— й”ҷиҜҜ\n\n#### и°ғиҜ•ж—Ҙеҝ—\n\nж— \n\n#### е®ҢжҲҗзҠ¶жҖҒ\n\nвҸі еҫ…ејҖе§Ӣ\n\n---\n\n### Job 7: ж–ҮжЎЈе’ҢзӨәдҫӢйӘҢиҜҒ\n\n#### зӣ®ж Ү\n\nйӘҢиҜҒж–ҮжЎЈе®Ңж•ҙжҖ§е’ҢзӨәдҫӢд»Јз ҒжӯЈзЎ®жҖ§\n\n#### еүҚзҪ®жқЎд»¶\n\n- job_6 - иҮӘжҲ‘йҮҚжһ„иғҪеҠӣйӘҢиҜҒе®ҢжҲҗ\n\n#### Tasks\n\n- [ ] Task 1: йӘҢиҜҒ README.md ж–ҮжЎЈе®Ңж•ҙ","numLines":50,"startLine":252,"totalLines":371}}},{"type":"assistant","message":{"role":"assistant","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"output_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0},"stop_reason":null,"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_757114b0-cf9","type":"message","content":[{"text":"Let me update the plan file with the debug log for Task 1:","type":"text"}],"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"54120658-0f38-420a-a12a-de4bb8dc43a6","uuid":"4cc18e15-61ad-4301-be53-b32cdb474670"},{"type":"assistant","message":{"role":"assistant","stop_sequenc